768
00:42:17,350 --> 00:42:18,270
Tak ada.

769
00:42:19,560 --> 00:42:20,430
Semangat!

770
00:42:23,190 --> 00:42:24,030
Kau sudah selesai bicara?

771
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:27,680
Ada yang gerak.

772
00:42:28,000 --> 00:42:29,880
Sudah bisa angkat pancingan, cepat.

773
00:42:30,520 --> 00:42:31,390
Tak bisa.

774
00:42:31,390 --> 00:42:32,760
Bukankah kau ingin belajar?

775
00:42:32,760 --> 00:42:33,680
Tak mau bangun.

776
00:42:35,960 --> 00:42:37,800
Bao paling suka makan ikan.

777
00:42:37,800 --> 00:42:38,880
Jika dia tahu ikan ini

778
00:42:38,880 --> 00:42:40,470
dipancing oleh Mamanya,

779
00:42:40,470 --> 00:42:41,640
dia pasti akan senang sekali.

780
00:42:44,070 --> 00:42:44,760
Cepat.

781
00:43:03,720 --> 00:43:04,880
Ikannya sudah terpancing.


